      <data key="d2">Elderwood Forest is an ancient forest that houses the Font of Resonance and many ancient trees.&lt;SEP&gt;Elderwood Forest is a forest near Aethelgard where the ruling council meets.&lt;SEP&gt;Elderwood Forest is where the ruling council of Eldoria meets.&lt;SEP&gt;Elderwood Forest is an ancient forest that houses the Font of Resonance and other natural features.</data>
