      <data key="d1">naturalobject</data>
      <data key="d2">Aethelite is a shimmering, crystalline substance found in rare geological formations, known for its lightness, brittleness, and interaction with ambient light.&lt;SEP&gt;Aethelite is a brittle element found in remote locations, known for its interaction with ambient light and luminescence storage.</data>
