    <node id="Pyron">
      <data key="d0">Pyron</data>
      <data key="d1">naturalobject</data>
      <data key="d2">Pyron is a highly volatile element that exists as a superheated, ionized gas, commonly found in regions of intense geothermal activity or electrical storms.&lt;SEP&gt;Pyron is a highly volatile element that exists as a superheated, ionized gas, commonly found in regions of intense geothermal activity or within planetary atmospheres undergoing significant electrical storms.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-1970ef43a0e81cfab9b4e349937d52ce&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5cea5faf4e8019e11b6d3c5f420f7267</data>
