      <data key="d1">phenomenon</data>
      <data key="d2">The localized zone is a side effect of producing Umbradium. It disrupts kinetic energy transfer and dampens electromagnetic fields.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-fdbdb9446200becfa82435a43d9650c2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6d17ad2ef72f49be20201bc489a66d62</data>
