    <edge source="World Athletics Federation" target="Noah Carter">
      <data key="d7">91.0</data>
      <data key="d8">The relationship between Noah Carter and the World Athletics Federation centers on the validation of Noah Carter's athletic record. The World Athletics Federation, the global governing body for athletics, has validated Noah Carter's record, signifying that it meets the federation's standards and criteria for authenticity and legitimacy. Formerly known as the International Association of Athletics Federations (IAAF), the World Athletics Federation oversees the regulations and recognition of athletic records worldwide. The validation process confirms that Noah Carter's achievement complies with established rules and procedures, underscoring its significance and credibility in the realm of athletics. This recognition by the World Athletics Federation highlights the importance of Noah Carter's record within the sport. The repeated validation by the federation underscores the consistency and reliability of this recognition.&lt;SEP&gt;Noah Carter's record is validated by the World Athletics Federation.&lt;SEP&gt;Noah Carter's record is validated by the World Athletics Federation.&lt;SEP&gt;Noah Carter's record is validated by the World Athletics Federation.&lt;SEP&gt;Noah Carter's record is validated by the World Athletics Federation.&lt;SEP&gt;Noah Carter's record is validated by the World Athletics Federation.&lt;SEP&gt;Noah Carter's record is validated by the World Athletics Federation.</data>
      <data key="d9">athlete recognition,record validation</data>
      <data key="d10">chunk-2d9f68ea236e65773d7fa8dfce96706b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-92fdd2272047e791e822f44a44a0aaa6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d5347c46fbfaa5dfb649cf5a7386a3e3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3ff616f8f6c6c72f501bacf6a84fb7d1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dbeb364cc8c11b8851ccc39994e900d3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-30032a9a218ee0319cc0b0104dbcb1fc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cb3d32acabcf93ff84d53e6c715f5868&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1eb2d3c42261f010e2d61a94fe10d597&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1d68c5e141612935adde70191b543400&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2e381bfb9255daea37fced8d1a9ca7e2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ca1ab38dd085858276b097adace00445&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0ec84394955e9010ff2eef03b888d02&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e090cc19fe61a5d57472585755cf3972&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-da5333743680ef3e99bf512f689a0a60&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9699258d651968b022029e2c5661bab9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9b5074b38cab28295111649885a53894&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e715408cde7e74b18571e02fbbf5a118&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dbfd518f3805f5b8ca795225dfe27c7e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2887778a6a2df3dfa6983170922380e7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f5993f98ef177a29e14efa7a1e0e1284&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f0749e4b55d29303cb6ae92ca3e8442e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8c0b33bdfde835b1b72a98108d2731c1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-df225153d9892c14a4f59cb36a4fdc52&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6334b4c5624e548f71327321342d3140&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b62a3a837a626d418867d6c09415f364&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-852b4aca9611d4ba02906005fe159143&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0398612496e142abad8c0525a7411b04&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-58a046875ebdee22cd2135d336e52823&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dacf097dab6d99b72c217adbf39a0e08&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ad901faf06a2cd13ee6b6629180f6ac5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-36c90a6ac7cf796320786dcff63fe321&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a8d5322c8953a45a40a65585c12dfa7d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ff92dbc05d0cbedece06bc3944fc2127&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-24dd209bf576ce21067d0019b17d1f19&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-24447252c282a0b1101534db7627da29&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-021b47fe4bc3c29da48ea2759bcc4e9f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-80ce62b82fbb9313903beadfa2b250e0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-26b571d9fdf386fb5cb2a12265c2bc78&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-33c4a997e02d1f9deac5d304cf96e2ed&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-db61661cef8af6791c007f451f13e085&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5e2e2feb3a7f